whenever you think of me.'

949
01:24:14,716 --> 01:24:16,411
'Feel proud, dear.'

950
01:24:40,776 --> 01:24:43,006
Your dream will surely be fulfilled.

951
01:24:43,445 --> 01:24:45,970
