markets in the world..

964
01:25:48,276 --> 01:25:51,370
..with a hope to find a
dealer who can get me..

965
01:25:51,480 --> 01:25:55,246
..a similar Romanian gold bar.

966
01:25:55,350 --> 01:25:56,840
