1023
01:30:22,584 --> 01:30:24,176
That's Spider. Trace it.

1024
01:30:24,285 --> 01:30:25,411
I am good, sir.

1025
01:30:25,487 --> 01:30:27,614
This time I've got a
really big order for you.

1026
01:30:27,922 --> 01:30:29,184
