confirm his exact location.

1039
01:30:51,279 --> 01:30:52,337
It's a confirmed order.

1040
01:30:52,447 --> 01:30:53,744
You checked their backgrounds.

1041
01:30:57,719 --> 01:30:59,482
Five seconds.
