1042
01:30:59,554 --> 01:31:01,317
What? You moron.

1043
01:31:01,422 --> 01:31:02,548
Three seconds.

1044
01:31:02,624 --> 01:31:03,784
But, sir..

1045
01:31:06,561 --> 01:31:09,621
